#. type: Content of: <p>
#: ../../skycultures/inuit/description.en.utf8:2
msgid ""
"The Inuit sky culture files available for Stellarium are an adaptation of "
"John MacDonald's research in his book <b>The Arctic Sky: Inuit Astronomy, "
